%% Model Registry - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.1/model-registry.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/Pipeline/CLI)
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>(kubeflow-gateway)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as Model Registry Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as InferenceService<br/>Controller<br/>8081/TCP
    participant CSI as CSI Storage<br/>Initializer
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/OCI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Job as Async Upload Job
    participant HF as Source Storage<br/>(HuggingFace/S3/OCI)

    Note over Client, DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward via VirtualService<br/>Istio mTLS (ISTIO_MUTUAL)
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT model metadata<br/>MySQL/PG protocol, Optional TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>Proxy: OK
    Proxy-->>Gateway: 201 Created (JSON)
    Gateway-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI, Proxy: Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService events<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Proxy: Sync metadata<br/>HTTP/8080, Optional TLS<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Proxy->>DB: Upsert inference service record
    DB-->>Proxy: OK
    Proxy-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService labels<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over CSI, Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading via CSI Storage Initializer
    CSI->>Proxy: GET model artifact URI<br/>HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>CSI: Artifact location (S3/OCI URI)
    CSI->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>Storage credentials

    Note over Job, Proxy: Flow 4: Async Model Upload
    Job->>HF: Download model<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>API Token / IAM
    HF-->>Job: Model artifacts
    Job->>Storage: Upload model<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS<br/>API Token / IAM
    Storage-->>Job: Upload complete
    Job->>Proxy: Register model artifact<br/>HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>Job: 201 Created
